  <h2 id="ben-ming-nian">Ben Ming Nian (本命年)</h2>

  <p>Your Ben Ming Nian (本命年 běn mìng nián) is when your zodiac year returns — every 12 years. Traditional belief holds that your Ben Ming Nian is an unlucky year because you are in conflict with the Tai Sui (太岁), the god who governs that year.</p>

  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin: 24px 0;">
    <div style="background: #fef2f2; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px;">
