      <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 0.95em;">
        <li>Wear red underwear all year</li>
        <li>Wear a red bracelet or belt</li>
        <li>Avoid big life changes if possible</li>
        <li>Visit a temple for blessings</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div style="background: #eff6ff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px;">
      <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e40af;">📅 Ben Ming Nian Ages</p>
