        <li>12, 24, 36, 48, 60, 72, 84...</li>
        <li>In 2026 (Horse year): people born in 2014, 2002, 1990, 1978...</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="five-elements">The Five Elements Connection</h2>

  <p>The Chinese zodiac actually operates on a 60-year cycle, not just 12. Each animal year combines with one of the five elements (五行 wǔxíng), creating unique variations:</p>

