        <td style="padding: 10px;">土 (tǔ)</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">Stability, patience, reliability</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px;">8, 9</td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="background: #f8fafc; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
